                "invention-title": [
                    "Solar seawater desalination hydrogen production refrigeration cycle system and method",
                    "一种太阳能海水淡化制氢制冷循环系统和方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of new energy, in particular to a solar seawater desalination, hydrogen production and refrigeration cycle system and method, and a solar heat collector performs photo-thermal conversion and transmits generated heat to a seawater desalination system, a water electrolysis hydrogen production system and a refrigeration cycle system through a first heat exchange box, a second heat exchange box and a third heat exchange box respectively. In the seawater desalination system, heat energy is absorbed through the heat transfer circulation pipeline and is transferred to the seawater distiller to generate steam, and then the steam is condensed by seawater, so that the energy consumption of multi-stage evaporative cooling in the seawater desalination process is saved. Purified water generated by seawater desalination is preheated through a second heat exchange box and then guided to the PEM electrolytic bath; purified water generated by the seawater desalination system cools the cooler, and cools the hydrogen cooler in the multi-stage compression cooling system after being cooled by the evaporator. The power consumption in the PEM water electrolysis hydrogen production and hydrogen storage process is saved, refrigeration can be achieved without using a high-power-consumption compressor, and the refrigeration energy consumption is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及新能源技术领域，尤其涉及一种太阳能海水淡化制氢制冷循环系统和方法，由太阳能集热器进行光热转换并将产生的热量分别通过第一换热箱、第二换热箱和第三换热箱传递至海水淡化系统、电解水制氢系统和制冷循环系统。海水淡化系统中通过传热循环管路吸收热能并传递至海水蒸馏器产生蒸汽，再由海水将蒸汽冷凝，节省了海水淡化过程中多级蒸发冷却的能耗。通过第二换热箱对海水淡化产生的纯净水进行预加热，再导向PEM电解槽；海水淡化系统产生的纯净水为冷却器降温，还通过蒸发器降温后为多级压缩冷系统中的氢气冷却器制冷。节省了PEM电解水制氢和储存氢气过程中的电量消耗，还可以不使用高功耗的压缩机实现制冷，降低制冷能耗。"
                }
